AutomaticPrepaymentApply is a BusinessTask
    owned by ar

    Patterns
        implements ManualTransaction
        implements StaticJava
            Reports
                AutomaticPrepaymentApplyReport

    Parameters
        Company                 is a ReceivableCompany 
        CompanyGroup            is a GeneralLedgerCompanyGroup                
        OprCode                 is a ReceivableOperator
        Customer                 
        CudName                 is AlphaUpper size 30

        ProcessLevel            is a ReceivableProcessLevel
        GlDate                  is Date
        OverRide                is AlphaUpper size 1
            States
                No  value is "N"
                Yes value is "Y"
		DisplayTransactionDate is Boolean
			default label is "DisplayTransactionDate"
    Parameter Rules
        CompanyGroup
            constraint (Company not entered)
            	"BothCompanyAndCompanyGroupCannotBeEntered"
            constraint (CompanyGroup.GeneralLedgerCompanyGroupMembersRel exists)
				"CompanyGroup<CompanyGroup>ContainsNoCompanies"
			constraint (ProcessLevel not entered)
				"CompanyRequiredForProcessLevel"
			constraint (Customer not entered)
				"CompanyRequiredForCustomer"
			constraint (OprCode not entered)
				"CompanyRequiredForOperator"
        OverRide
        	initial value is "N"
            default to "N"

    Actions
        AutomaticPrepaymentApply is a Set Action
